    <div class="buddha-section">
      <h1 class="heading">The Moment of Enlightenment</h1>
      <p class="body">As the morning star rose on that fateful day, Siddhartha experienced a profound transformation. He had transcended ignorance and desire, attaining supreme wisdom and compassion. He became the Buddha, meaning "The Enlightened One."

        The enlightenment of Siddhartha Gautama was not just a personal triumph but a universal breakthrough that offered humanity a path to liberation from suffering. The Buddha's realization was rooted in the understanding that suffering arises from craving and attachment and that liberation is possible through ethical conduct, mental discipline, and wisdom..</p>
